@{bg shine}Distribution of Mathador@{bg back}

@{b}@{fg shine}Mathador is (C) Dr.Werner Mayr 1996-1997.@{ub}@{fg text}

Mathador is SHAREWARE. It is NOT public domain. The @{"author" link "how_to_contact" 0} gives permission
for Mathador to be freely distributed providing that no commercial gain is
made from its distribution, and no modification is made to the original
distribution.

Organisations or people wishing to include Mathador on a coverdisk or CD-ROM
should contact me first to sort out the details. This EXCLUDES the AMINET
CD-ROM or Fred Fish CD-ROM collections.

@{b}DISCLAIMER@{ub}

This software is provided "as-is" and the author accepts no responsibility for
damage and/or loss of data/equipment resulting from the use of this software.
(not that it's very likely! ;-})

@{b}COST@{ub}

Only a few features of Mathador are crippled to allow you to appreciate the
program nearly to the full. If you keep Mathador for more than an evaluation
period and to get the full version on an original disk please send the
shareware fee to the author. You should print out the "@{"OrderForm" link "orderform" 0}"-file for
that purpose, fill it in and send it to me. Please send the fee either in
cash, Eurocheque, Postal Money Order or Money transfer to my account.


    Shareware fee:

