        ÖS             210,-

        (or equivalent in currency)

    Contact address:

        Dr.Werner Mayr
        Julius Willerthgasse 18/5
        A-2700 Wiener Neustadt
        Austria

        email: werner.mayr@univie.ac.at


Please pay the fee: Mathador has taken a LOT of my valuable time. Consider how
much time you are saving yourself by using it! Paying the fee will really
encourage me to continue developing Mathador.

As an alternative to paying the fee, if you've written any *decent* Shareware
yourself send me a registered copy (by snail-mail, or UUencode an LHA archive
and email it to @{"me" link "how_to_contact" 0}).
